{"title_page": "List of zoos by country", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis is a list of '''zoological gardens''' ([[zoo]]s) around the world. For [[Public aquarium|aquaria]], see [[List of aquaria]]. For [[dolphinarium]]s, see [[List of dolphinariums]]. For an annotated list of defunct zoos and aquariums, see [[List of former zoos and aquariums]].\n\nZoos are primarily dry facilities where animals are kept within enclosures and displayed to the public, and in which they may also be bred. Such facilities include [[zoo]]s, [[safari park]]s, [[animal theme park]]s, [[aviary|aviaries]], [[butterfly zoo]]s and [[herpetarium|reptile centers]], as well as [[wildlife sanctuary|wildlife sanctuaries]] and [[nature reserve]]s where visitors are allowed.\n{{TOC right|limit=3}}\n\n==Africa==\n\n===[[Algeria]]===\n*[[Algiers Zoo]]\n*[[Jijel Zoo]]\n*[[Oran Zoo]]\n\n===[[Burkina Faso]]===\n*[[Ouagadougou Zoo]]\n\n===[[Cameroon]]===\n*[[Mvog-Betsi Zoo]] - [[Yaound\u00e9]]\n\n===[[Congo DR|Congo, Democratic Republic of the]]===\n*[[Jardin Zoologique et Botanique d'Eala]]\n*[[Parc Zoologique de Lubumbashi]]\n*[[Zoo National de Kinshasa]]\n\n===[[Republic of the Congo|Congo, Republic of the]]===\n*[[Brazzaville Zoo]]\n\n===[[Ivory Coast]]===\n*[[Abidjan Zoo]]\n\n===[[Egypt]]===\n*[[Alexandria Zoo]]\n*[[Giza Zoo]]\n*[[Qariyet El Assad]] (Lions' Village)\n*[[Tanta Zoo]]\n*[[Mansoura Zoo]]\n*[[New Cairo Zoo]]\n*[[Beni Sweif Zoo]]\n*[[Alfayoum Zoo]]\n*[[Africano Park]]\n\n===[[Ethiopia]]===\n*[[Addis Ababa Lion Zoo]]\n\n===[[Ghana]]===\n*[[Kumasi Zoo]]\n\n===[[Kenya]]===\n*[[Mwaluganje Elephant Sanctuary]] - [[Kwale District]], [[Coast Province]]\n\n===[[Libya]]===\n*[[Tripoli Zoo]] - [[Tripoli]]\n*[[Benghazi Zoo]] (''\"Il bosco\" '') - [[Benghazi]]\n\n===[[Madagascar]]===\n*[[Tsimbazaza Zoo]] - [[Antananarivo]]\n*[[Croc Farm]] - Antananarivo\n*[[Lemur's Park|Lemurs' Park]] - near [[Antananarivo]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lemurspark.com/|title=L\u00e9muriens \u00e0 Madagascar Pr\u00e9sentation du Lemurs Park - Lemurs park|website=www.lemurspark.com|access-date=2009-04-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SjzY3qYM?url=http://www.lemurspark.com/|archive-date=2014-09-21|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[Parc Ivoloina]] - [[Toamasina]]\n*[[Madagascar Exotic]] - Marozevo\n*[[Parc Endemika]] - Sainte-Marie\n\n===[[Malawi]]===\n* [[Blantyre Zoological Gardens]]\n\n===[[Mali]]===\n*[[Bamako Zoo]]\n\n===[[Mauritius]]===\n*[[La Vanille Nature Park]]\n*[[Casela Nature Park]]\n\n===[[Morocco]]===\n*[http://dreamvillage.ma/ Dream Village] Dream Village\n*[http://www.jardinsexotiques.com/ Exotiques de Bouknadel]\n*[http://rabatzoo.ma/ Zoologique de Rabat] [[Rabat Zoo|Jardin Zoologique]] de [[Rabat]]\n\n===[[Mozambique]]===\n*[http://www.zoomaputo.org/] - [[Maputo Zoo]]\n\n===[[Nigeria]]===\n* [[Abuja Children's Zoo]] - [[Abuja]]\n* [[Audu Bako Zoo]] - [[Kano]]\n* [[Enugu Zoo]] - [[Enugu]]\n* [[Ibadan University Zoo]] - [[Ibadan]]\n* [[Jos Wildlife Park]]\n* [[Ogba Zoo]] - [[Benin City]]\n* [[Port Harcourt Zoo]] - [[Port Harcourt]]\n* [[Sanda Kyarimi Zoo]] - [[Maiduguri]]\n* [[FUNAAB Zoo]] -[[Abeokuta]]\n\n===[[Senegal]]===\n*[[Parcs Forestier et Zoologique de Hann]] - [[Dakar]]\n\n===[[South Africa]]===\n*[[Bester Birds and Animals Zoo Park]]\n*[[Birds of Eden]]\n*[[Bloemfontein Zoo]]\n*[[East London Zoological Gardens]]\n*[[EndoFaun Zoological Gardens]] - [[Bapsfontein]]\n*[[The Elephant Sanctuary Plettenberg Bay]] - [[Plettenberg Bay]]<ref>[http://www.elephantsanctuary.co.za/cragshome.htm The Elephant Sanctuary Plettenberg Bay] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229205743/http://www.elephantsanctuary.co.za/cragshome.htm |date=2010-12-29 }}</ref>\n*[[The Elephant Sanctuary Hartbeespoort Dam]] - [[Hartbeespoort Dam]]<ref>[http://www.elephantsanctuary.co.za/hartieshome.htm The Elephant Sanctuary Hartbeespoort Dam] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117185401/http://www.elephantsanctuary.co.za/hartie