]] - [[Iquitos]], [[Loreto Region|Loreto]]\n*[[Parque de las Leyendas]], [[San Miguel District, Lima|San Miguel]], [[Lima]]\n*[[Parque Zool\u00f3gico de Huachipa]] - [[Ate District|Ate]], [[Lima]]\n*[[Zoocriadero]] - [[Lima]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ci.edu.pe/|title=Portal del Colegio de la Inmaculada|website=www.ci.edu.pe|access-date=2011-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910023856/http://www.ci.edu.pe/|archive-date=2011-09-10|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n===[[Uruguay]]===\n* [[Pan de Az\u00facar Nature Reserve]] - [[Cerro Pan de Az\u00facar]]\n* [[Parque Lecocq]] - [[Montevideo]]\n* [[Zool\u00f3gico Municipal Villa Dolores]] - [[Montevideo]]\n\n===[[Venezuela]]===\n*[[Parque Zool\u00f3gico y Bot\u00e1nico Bararida]] - [[Parque Zool\u00f3gico y Bot\u00e1nico Bararida]]\n*[[Bararida Zoo]] - [[Bararida]]\n\n==Well-known people with private zoos==\n*[[Jorge Hank Rhon]]\n*[[Michael Jackson]] - at [[Neverland Ranch]]\n*[[Uday Hussein]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n===Sources===\n*{{cite web\n |url         = http://www.zoos-worldwide.de\n |title       = Zoos Worldwide: Aquariums, Animal Sanctuaries, and Wildlife Parks\n |work        = zoos-worldwide.de\n |publisher   = Zoos Worldwide\n |accessdate  = 2 July 2011\n |url-status     = dead\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20110719115732/http://www.zoos-worldwide.de/\n |archivedate = 19 July 2011\n}}\n\n{{Expand list|date=August 2008}}\n\n{{Zoos}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Zoos}}\n[[Category:Lists of buildings and structures]]\n[[Category:Zoos by country| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of zoos| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis is a list of '''zoological gardens''' ([[zoo]]s) around the world. For [[Public aquarium|aquaria]], see [[List of aquaria]]. For [[dolphinarium]]s, see [[List of dolphinariums]]. For an annotated list of defunct zoos and aquariums, see [[List of former zoos and aquariums]].\n\nZoos are primarily dry facilities where animals are kept within enclosures and displayed to the public, and in which they may also be bred. Such facilities include [[zoo]]s, [[safari park]]s, [[animal theme park]]s, [[aviary|aviaries]], [[butterfly zoo]]s and [[herpetarium|reptile centers]], as well as [[wildlife sanctuary|wildlife sanctuaries]] and [[nature reserve]]s where visitors are allowed.\n{{TOC right|limit=3}}\n\n==Africa==\n\n===[[Algeria]]===\n*[[Algiers Zoo]]\n*[[Jijel Zoo]]\n*[[Oran Zoo]]\n\n===[[Burkina Faso]]===\n*[[Ouagadougou Zoo]]\n\n===[[Cameroon]]===\n*[[Mvog-Betsi Zoo]] - [[Yaound\u00e9]]\n\n===[[Congo DR|Congo, Democratic Republic of the]]===\n*[[Jardin Zoologique et Botanique d'Eala]]\n*[[Parc Zoologique de Lubumbashi]]\n*[[Zoo National de Kinshasa]]\n\n===[[Republic of the Congo|Congo, Republic of the]]===\n*[[Brazzaville Zoo]]\n\n===[[Ivory Coast]]===\n*[[Abidjan Zoo]]\n\n===[[Egypt]]===\n*[[Alexandria Zoo]]\n*[[Giza Zoo]]\n*[[Qariyet El Assad]] (Lions' Village)\n*[[Tanta Zoo]]\n*[[Mansoura Zoo]]\n*[[New Cairo Zoo]]\n*[[Beni Sweif Zoo]]\n*[[Alfayoum Zoo]]\n*[[Africano Park]]\n\n===[[Ethiopia]]===\n*[[Addis Ababa Lion Zoo]]\n\n===[[Ghana]]===\n*[[Kumasi Zoo]]\n\n===[[Kenya]]===\n*[[Mwaluganje Elephant Sanctuary]] - [[Kwale District]], [[Coast Province]]\n\n===[[Libya]]===\n*[[Tripoli Zoo]] - [[Tripoli]]\n*[[Benghazi Zoo]] (''\"Il bosco\" '') - [[Benghazi]]\n\n===[[Madagascar]]===\n*[[Tsimbazaza Zoo]] - [[Antananarivo]]\n*[[Croc Farm]] - Antananarivo\n*[[Lemur's Park|Lemurs' Park]] - near [[Antananarivo]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lemurspark.com/|title=L\u00e9muriens \u00e0 Madagascar Pr\u00e9sentation du Lemurs Park - Lemurs park|website=www.lemurspark.com|access-date=2009-04-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SjzY3qYM?url=http://www.lemurspark.com/|archive-date=2014-09-21|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[Parc Ivoloina]] - [[Toamasina]]\n*[[Madagascar Exotic]] - Marozevo\n*[[Parc Endemika]] - Sainte-Marie\n\n===[[Malawi]]===\n* [[Blantyre Zoological Gardens]]\n\n===[[Mali]]===\n*[[Bamako Zoo]]\n\n===[[M