alakhel]]\n\n===[[Pakistan]]===\n*[[List of zoos in Pakistan]]\n\n===[[Palestinian territories]]===\n\n*[[Gaza Zoo]] - [[Gaza City|Gaza]]\n*[[Qalqilya Zoo]] - [[West Bank]]\n\n===[[Philippines]]===\n*[[Albay Park and Wildlife]] - [[Legazpi, Albay]]<ref>[http://tourism.albay.gov.ph/apwl.htm/ Albay Park and Wildlife] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629190733/http://tourism.albay.gov.ph/apwl.htm |date=2011-06-29 }}</ref>\n*[[Animal Island (zoo)]] - Binakayan, [[Kawit, Cavite]]<ref>[http://www.islandcovephil.com/activities/play-3/ Animal Island] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925123155/http://www.islandcovephil.com/activities/play-3/ |date=2011-09-25 }}</ref>\n*[[Animal Wonderland]] - [[Star City (amusement park)|Star City]], [[Pasay]]\n*[[Ark Avilon Zoo]] - Frontera Verde, Ortigas Avenue, [[Pasig]]\n*[[Ave Maria Sanctuary and Park]] - [[Carcar]], [[Cebu]]\n*[[Avilon Zoo]] - [[Rodriguez, Rizal]]\n*[[Baluarte Zoo]] - [[Vigan]], [[Ilocos Sur]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chavitsingson.net/baluarte/index.html/|title=Baluarte Zoo|access-date=2011-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114112259/http://chavitsingson.net/baluarte/index.html|archive-date=2016-11-14|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n*[[Birds International]] - [[Quezon City]]\n*[[Botolan Wildlife Farm]] - San Juan, [[Botolan, Zambales]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.botolanwildlifefarm.com/|title=Botolan Wildlife Farm Zambales|website=www.botolanwildlifefarm.com|access-date=2011-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911021056/http://www.botolanwildlifefarm.com/|archive-date=2011-09-11|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n*[[Calauit Safari Park]] - Calauit Island, [[Palawan]]\n*[[Cavite City Zoological and Botanical Park]] - Sampaguita Road, Seabreeze Subdivision, Santa Cruz, [[Cavite City]], [[Cavite]]\n*[[Cebu City Zoo and Conservation Zoo]] - Calunasan, [[Cebu City]], [[Cebu]]\n*[[Corregidor Aviary and Theme Park]] - [[Corregidor Island]], [[Cavite]]\n*[[Crocolandia F