ore]]\n*[[River Safari]]\n*[[List of former zoos and aquariums#Singapore Crocodile Farm|Singapore Crocodile Farm]] (closed 2012)\n*[[Singapore Zoo]]\n\n===[[Sri Lanka]]===\n*[[Ahungalla Animal Park]]\n*[[Dehiwala Zoo]]\n*[[Pinnawala Elephant Orphanage]]\n*[[Pinnawala Elephant Safari]]<ref>[http://pinnawalasafari.com/ Pinnawala Elephant Safari] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904021108/http://pinnawalasafari.com/ |date=2013-09-04 }}</ref>\n*[[Pinnawela Open Zoo]]\n*[[hambantota safari zoo]]\n*[[Wagolla zoo]]\n*[[battaramulla mini zoo]]\n\n===[[Taiwan]]===\n*[[Taipei Zoo]] - [[Taipei]]\n*[[Kaohsiung Zoo]]\n*[[Green World Ecological Farm]]\n*[[1-Lan Wild Animal Rescue Centre]]\n*[[Far East Animal Farm]]\n*[[Feng-Hung-Ku Bird Park]]\n*[[Hsinchu City Zoo]]\n*[[Leefoo Zoo]]\n*[[National Museum of Marine Biology/Aquarium]]\n*[[Ocean World (Taiwan)|Ocean World]] - [[Yehliu Wanli]]\n*[[Pintung Rescue Centre]]\n\n===[[Thailand]]===\n*[[Chiang Mai Night Safari]]\n*[[Chiang Mai Zoo]]\n*[[Crocodiles Farm and Elephant Theme Show Sampran]] - [[Nakorn Pathom]]\n*[[Samutprakarn Crocodile Farm and Zoo]]\n*[[Dusit Zoo]] (closed 2018)\n*[[Chaiyaphum Star Tiger Zoo]]\n*[[Elephant Nature Park]] - [[Chiang Mai Province]]\n*[[Khao Kheow Open Zoo]]\n*[[Khao Suan Kwang Zoo]] - [[Khon Kaen]]\n*[[Khao Prathap Chang Wildlife Breeding Center]] - [[Ratchaburi]]\n*[[Lopburi Zoo]]\n*[[Nakhon Ratchasima Zoo]]\n*[[Nong Nooch Tropical Botanical Garden]]\n*[[Pata Zoo]] - [[Bangkok]]\n*[[Phuket Zoo]] - [[Phuket (city)|Phuket]]\n*[[Phuket bird park]] - [[Phuket]]\n*[[Safari Park Kanchanaburi]] - [[Kanchanaburi]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.safaripark-kan.com/|title=SAFARI PARK OPEN ZOO & CAMP BOPHLOI KANCHANABURI : \u0e04\u0e48\u0e32\u0e22\u0e1e\u0e31\u0e01\u0e41\u0e23\u0e21,camp,Kanchanaburi,zoo,nature,siam.thailand,Safari Park Open Zoo & Camp|website=www.safaripark-kan.com|access-date=2011-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510081528/http://www.safaripark-kan.com/|ar